headlines.description: Wolverhampton Wanderers had a goal by Leander Dendoncker ruled out by VAR in an entertaining 0-0 Premier League draw at Leicester City.
headlines.shortLinkText: VAR denies Wolves victory at Leicester

headlines.description: Arsenal struggled to a 1-0 victory over Newcastle in their Premier League season opener at St. James' Park on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Aubameyang strike edges Arsenal past Newcastle

headlines.description: Marcus Rashford scored two with Anthony Martial and Daniel James also on the scoresheet to earn Man United an emphatic 4-0 victory over Chelsea.
headlines.shortLinkText: Man Utd hammer Chelsea with Rashford double
